      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented version control, regression testing, and release validation for blood flow applications.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 employed with documented V&V test suite. Software release notes confirm regression test pass rate >99.8%. Version control via institutional repository with audit trail. Meets MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
