      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification must confirm correct numerical implementation through benchmark problems relevant to rotating machinery and viscous flow.",
      "rationale": "Solver verified against Taylor-Couette flow and lid-driven cavity benchmarks. Manufactured solution test confirms second-order spatial accuracy. Code verification artifacts archived and traceable to solver release documentation."
