      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must be documented with sufficient detail to allow computational reproduction, including fluid properties, boundary conditions, and operating point specifications.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental data (Hariharan et al. 2011) provides complete documentation of flow rates (2–7 L/min), rotational speeds (2000–3500 RPM), and blood analog fluid properties. Boundary conditions reproduced computationally with <1% deviation from reported experimental values."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
