      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index RH compared across all 5 operating points. Mean absolute percentage error 8.3%; normalized index of agreement 0.91. Pressure-flow characteristic curves match experimental data within 5% across full operating range. All acceptance criteria satisfied."
