      "rationale": "Validation conducted on FDA generic centrifugal blood pump — the standard benchmark for CPB CFD validation. Operating conditions span the full COU envelope (2–7 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Blood analog fluid (glycerin-water, matched viscosity) used in experiments. Geometric similarity confirmed by independent mesh comparison. Validation relevance rated high for MRL 2."
