      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for Class II device with medium model influence.",
      "rationale": "Use error assessment not required at MRL 2. Analyst qualifications documented (5+ years CFD blood pump experience). Standard operating procedures followed for mesh generation, boundary condition specification, and post-processing. No formal use error quantification required at this risk level."
    },
