      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form selection must be justified with reference to literature or prior validation evidence for hemolysis prediction in rotary blood pumps.",
      "rationale": "RANS k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on published benchmark comparisons (Stewart et al. 2012, Hariharan et al. 2011) demonstrating superior performance in rotating blood pump geometries. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power law validated against in-vitro data. Model form uncertainty acknowledged as dominant uncertainty source at MRL 2; quantitative bounding not required."
    },
    {
