      "rationale": "Fluid properties (density 1056 kg/m3, viscosity 0.0035 Pa·s) sourced from published blood analog characterization. Geometric inputs derived from FDA benchmark CAD with dimensional tolerances ±0.05 mm. Boundary conditions (inlet flow rate, outlet pressure, rotational speed) specified from experimental protocol. Input traceability matrix documented."
